author: Vertyco
description: Create backups of your Discord server and restore them easily
end_user_data_statement:
This cog stores information about your entire discord server including user IDs.
**NOTE**
Restoring backups can be rate-limit intensive, and may take quite a while.
install_msg:
Thank you for installing! Use the `[p]cargorapherset` command to view the settings.

THIS COG IS NOT INTENDED FOR PUBLIC BOTS! SERVER BACKUPS TAKE UP A LOT OF SPACE AND CAN BE RATE-LIMIT INTENSIVE!
